en:
The panoramic restaurant La Source overlooks the ocean and offers a cuisine full of imagination, rooted in the culinary heritage of the Pays de la Loire. Surprising textures and associations, modern and refined for an explosion of flavors in the mouth.
The menu is varied and different according to the seasons.

Every Thursday, the restaurant proposes a seafood evening which is composed in the following way: plate of Seafood (at discretion), plate of cheeses, dessert in the choice in the card of the day.

